{"title":"万里长江第一弯①","authors":["顾浩"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":9,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长江第一弯①"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾浩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伫立曲岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正秋江雨歇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临水思远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洲草垂首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堤树支颔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山高处求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻燕轻声探。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一弯百解，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直搅得风急云乱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真谛哪里读？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪涛千卷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万古长流浩瀚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪波滚滚是忧患！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五十世纪来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母河恩深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炎黄薪火传！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华英才辈出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明星历历多璀璨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试与问："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假使当初南去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司马怎撰？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：①长江上游金沙江，由北向南流经云南丽江地区石鼓镇，突折向东北流，这里就是著名的“万里长江第一弯”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"②司马，指西汉史学家、文学家、思想家司马迁。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}